Pair<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> getBuffer()

setAbnormalExitStatus

void setAbnormalExitStatus(int status)

setBuffer

void setBuffer(Pair<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> buffer)

The buffer can only be set once in each command execution.
